prompts.frontCover: A minimalist 2D cartoon greeting card front. A charming, slightly grumpy cartoon avocado is sitting on the floor, its large seed-belly prominently displayed. Next to the avocado is a single, brightly lit birthday candle, stuck into a tiny cupcake that is almost comically small compared to the avocado. The avocado has its little arms crossed and is looking at the single candle with a deadpan, unimpressed expression. The background is a clean, solid pastel cream color. Centered above the scene, in an elegant, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "I got you a cake. It's the thought that counts." The overall style is clean, simple, with elegant shapes and a lighthearted, humorous feel.
